[2;36m                    [0m         process did not complete its execution within the allotted time limit.              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ## Description                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         - Issue Overview                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m           The libFuzzer engine aborted a fuzzing session due to a timeout. This means that  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         the fuzzer‚Äôs execution exceeded the predefined time threshold without completing    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         its test iteration.                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         - Vulnerability Type                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m           No explicit vulnerability type is specified in the report. The timeout error      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         itself points to an operational or performance issue during fuzz testing rather     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         than a direct security flaw.                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         - Important Observations and Findings                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m           ‚Ä¢ The error message ‚ÄúERROR: libFuzzer: timeout‚Äù signals that the fuzz target did  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         not return control to libFuzzer in time.                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m           ‚Ä¢ The timeout occurred in the context of an automated fuzzing harness, which      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         serves as the entry point for test inputs.                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m           ‚Ä¢ There is no indication in the report of crashes, memory corruption, or          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         sanitizer reports‚Äîonly that the session timed out.                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m           ‚Ä¢ The absence of other error diagnostics suggests that the code under test may be [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         stuck in a long‚Äêrunning loop, blocking call, or resource-intensive computation when [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         given certain inputs.                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         - Code Areas to Investigate                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m           [1;36m1[0m. Fuzzing Harness Entry Point                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              Review how inputs are fed into the target functions and whether the harness    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         imposes any timeouts or watchdog controls.                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m           [1;36m2[0m. Core Processing Functions                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              Identify functions or loops in the codebase that process fuzzer-generated data [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         and could potentially run indefinitely or perform extensive work.                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m           [1;36m3[0m. I/O and Blocking Operations                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              Examine any file, network, or synchronization calls that might block or wait   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         for external events.                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m           [1;36m4[0m. Resource-Intensive Algorithms                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              Look at algorithms with unbounded loops or recursive calls that scale with     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         input size.                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m           [1;36m5[0m. Timeout Configuration                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              Check libFuzzer flags and environment settings to confirm the configured       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         timeout value and ensure it aligns with expected execution times.                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         By focusing on these areas, a comprehensive view of why the fuzzing session timed   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         out can be achieved without presuming the underlying cause.                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ## Initial Issue Log                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         Here is the initial issue log of the codebase:                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1m<[0m[1;95missue[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95missue[0m[39m>[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Analysis [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Analysis Report[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Relevant Code Snippets[0m                                                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m231[0m[39m:    public static PDDocument [0m[1;35mload[0m[1;39m([0m[39mFile file, String password[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m232[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m233[0m[39m:        return [0m[1;35mLoader.loadPDF[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfile, password[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m234[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m235[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m236[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/PDFParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:100[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m140[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m100[0m[39m:     * at the beginning of the file. Last the root object is parsed.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m101[0m[39m:     * [0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m102[0m[39m:     * @throws InvalidPasswordException If the password is incorrect.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m103[0m[39m:     * @throws IOException If something went wrong.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m104[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m105[0m[39m:    protected void [0m[1;35minitialParse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m106[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m107[0m[39m:        COSDictionary trailer = [0m[1;35mretrieveTrailer[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m108[0m[39m:    [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m109[0m[39m:        COSDictionary root = [0m[1;35mtrailer.getCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName.ROOT[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m110[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mroot == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m111[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m112[0m[39m:            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Missing root object specification in [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mtrailer."[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m113[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m114[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m in some pdfs the type value [0m[32m"Catalog"[0m[39m is missing in the root object[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m115[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35misLenient[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m && ![0m[1;35mroot.containsKey[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName.TYPE[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m116[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m117[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mroot.setItem[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName.TYPE, COSName.CATALOG[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m118[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m119[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m check pages dictionaries[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m120[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mcheckPages[0m[1;39m([0m[39mroot[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m121[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mdocument.setDecrypted[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m122[0m[39m:        initialParseDone = true;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m123[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m124[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m125[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m126[0m[39m:     * This will parse the stream and populate the PDDocument object. This will[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mclose the keystore stream when it is[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m127[0m[39m:     * done parsing. Lenient mode is active by default.[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m128[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m129[0m[39m:     * @return the populated PDDocument[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m130[0m[39m:     *[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m131[0m[39m:     * @throws InvalidPasswordException If the password is incorrect.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m132[0m[39m:     * @throws IOException If there is an error reading from the stream or [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorrupt data is found.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m133[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m134[0m[39m:    public PDDocument [0m[1;35mparse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m135[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m136[0m[39m:        return [0m[1;35mparse[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtrue[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m137[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m138[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m139[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m140[0m[39m:     * This will parse the stream and populate the PDDocument object. This will[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mclose the keystore stream when it is[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Identify and isolate the unbounded‚Äêloop in stream parsing  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The core culprit is BaseParser.parseCOSStream [0m[1;39m([0m[39min BaseParser.java[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. It reads [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mraw stream data from the fuzzer input in a loop, repeatedly scanning for the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m‚Äúendstream‚Äù marker with lastIndexOf, but never gives up if the marker is missing. [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mOn fuzzed or malformed inputs [0m[1;39m([0m[39mespecially ones without a valid [0m[35m/[0m[95mLength[0m[39m or without [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39man ‚Äúendstream‚Äù delimiter[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, this loop can read until EOF ad infinitum, causing [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibFuzzer to hang and eventually time out.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Introduce a maximum‚Äêscan guard in parseCOSStream  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Before entering the read/scan loop, retrieve the declared stream length from [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe COSStream dictionary [0m[1;39m([0m[39mif present[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ‚Ä¢ COSBase lengthObj = [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mcurrentStreamDictionary.getDictionaryObject[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSName.LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ‚Ä¢ If lengthObj is a valid COSNumber [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdirect or indirect[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, extract long [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeclaredLength = [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mCOSNumber[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m lengthObj[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.longValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Define a scan limit:  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ‚Ä¢ If declaredLength > [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, set maxScanBytes = declaredLength + markerOverhead [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39me.g. [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ‚Ä¢ Else [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno or invalid [0m[35m/[0m[95mLength[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, fall back to a configurable global cap, e.g. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMAX_STREAM_SCAN = 10_000_000 [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m10[0m[39m MB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m or a system‚Äêproperty override.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. In the main read‚Äêand‚Äêscan loop, maintain a running total of bytesRead. After [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39meach read/append/scan iteration, if totalBytesRead > maxScanBytes, break the loop [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand throw an [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Missing 'endstream' marker within X bytes"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to fail fast.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Fail fast on EOF  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure that if [0m[1;35msource.read[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m returns ‚Äì[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mEOF[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, the loop terminates [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimmediately and throws a clear IOException rather than continuing to spin.[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Prevent unbounded page‚Äêtree recursion in checkPages  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In PDFParser.checkPages [0m[1;39m([0m[39min PDFParser.java[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, add cycle detection and a maximum[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdepth guard to avoid infinite recursion on malicious page trees:  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     a. Overload checkPages to accept a Set<COSDictionary> visitedPages and a depth[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcounter.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     b. On each invocation, if the current COSDictionary is already in [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvisitedPages, return immediately.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     c. If depth > MAX_PAGE_TREE_DEPTH [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m [0m[1;36m000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, throw [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Page tree [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mtoo deep or cyclic"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to abort.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     d. Otherwise, add the current dictionary to visitedPages and recurse on all [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchild page dictionaries under [0m[35m/[0m[95mKids.[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Preserve existing functionality  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - All valid PDFs with correct [0m[35m/[0m[95mLength[0m[39m entries and proper ‚Äúendstream‚Äù delimiters [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwill never exceed their declaredLength+overhead, so the new guard does not affect [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnormal behavior.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The global cap only applies when no [0m[35m/[0m[95mLength[0m[39m is provided [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmost well‚Äêformed PDFs[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mspecify a length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Cycle detection in page trees only catches truly malformed or malicious [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcycles; well‚Äêformed trees are acyclic and shallow.[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Implementation steps  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. In BaseParser.java, locate parseCOSStream implementation.  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Add code before the stream‚Äêread loop to fetch and normalize the [0m[35m/[0m[95mLength[0m[39m value[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mdereferencing indirect objects if needed[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Define constants [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. [0m[33mDEFAULT_MAX_STREAM_SCAN[0m[39m=[0m[35m10_000_000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and a system [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mproperty [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. ‚Äúpdfbox.stream.parse.maxBytes‚Äù[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to allow overridable limits.  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d. Wrap the existing byte‚Äêread loop with a byte‚Äêcounter check. On exceeding the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcap, break and throw.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   e. Ensure that EOF [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35msource.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m also triggers loop exit and a clean [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexception.  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   f. In PDFParser.java, refactor checkPages to add the visited‚Äêset and depth [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchecks as described.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Testing and side‚Äêeffect mitigation  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add unit tests feeding small synthetic PDFs without [0m[35m/[0m[95mLength[0m[39m or without [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mendstream to confirm immediate failure instead of hang.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run existing PDFBox test suite to verify no regressions on well‚Äêformed PDFs of[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvarying sizes and stream types.  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Tune DEFAULT_MAX_STREAM_SCAN upward if any real‚Äêworld PDF in the test suite [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexceeds [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m MB uncompressed in a single stream.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Document the new system property and its recommended bounds for large‚Äêstream [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muse cases.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m8[0m[39m. Justification  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This strategy directly addresses the root cause [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe unbounded marker‚Äêscan [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloop[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m without touching external libs, harness code, or test code.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - It leverages PDF spec semantics [0m[1;39m([0m[35m/[0m[95mLength[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to set a sane bound and falls back [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto a global cap on malformed inputs.  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Cycle detection in checkPages is a lightweight guard that prevents page‚Äêtree [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDoS without altering normal traversal logic.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Similar patterns exist elsewhere in PDFBox [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. readStringNumber enforces a [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmax digit count[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, so introducing a max‚Äêbytes check is consistent with library [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstyle.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No existing functionality is removed or weakened; valid PDFs parse correctly, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmalformed ones fail fast, and fuzzing runs complete instead of timing out.[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m191[0m[39m:            [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m in the middle of the keyword, see PDFBOX-[0m[1;36m3936[0m[39m.[0m                   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m175[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mpdDocument.setEncryptionDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mgetEncryption[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m176[0m[39m:            return pdDocument;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m177[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m178[0m[39m:        finally[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m179[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m180[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mexceptionOccurred && document != null[0m[1;39m)[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/BruteForceParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:130[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m160[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m130[0m[39m:     * @throws IOException if something went wrong[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m131[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m132[0m[39m:    private void [0m[1;35mbfSearchForObjects[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m133[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m134[0m[39m:        long lastEOFMarker = [0m[1;35mbfSearchForLastEOFMarker[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m135[0m[39m:        long originOffset = [0m[1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m136[0m[39m:        long currentOffset = MINIMUM_SEARCH_OFFSET;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m137[0m[39m:        long lastObjectId = Long.MIN_VALUE;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m138[0m[39m:        int lastGenID = Integer.MIN_VALUE;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m139[0m[39m:        long lastObjOffset = Long.MIN_VALUE;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m140[0m[39m:        char[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m endobjString = [0m[32m"ndo"[0m[1;35m.toCharArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m141[0m[39m:        char[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m endobjRemainingString = [0m[32m"bj"[0m[1;35m.toCharArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m142[0m[39m:        boolean endOfObjFound = false;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m143[0m[39m:        do[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m144[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m145[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35msource.seek[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcurrentOffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m146[0m[39m:            int nextChar = [0m[1;35msource.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m147[0m[39m:            currentOffset++;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m148[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mBaseParser.isWhitespace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnextChar[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m && [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mparser.isString[0m[1;39m([0m[39mOBJ_MARKER[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m149[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m150[0m[39m:                long tempOffset = currentOffset - [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m151[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35msource.seek[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtempOffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m152[0m[39m:                int genID = [0m[1;35msource.peek[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m153[0m[39m:                [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m is the next char a digit?[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m154[0m[39m:                if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mBaseParser.isDigit[0m[1;39m([0m[39mgenID[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m155[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m156[0m[39m:                    genID -= [0m[1;36m48[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m157[0m[39m:                    tempOffset--;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m158[0m[39m:                    [0m[1;35msource.seek[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtempOffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m159[0m[39m:                    if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mparser.isWhitespace[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m160[0m[39m:                    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/PDFParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:236[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m236[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m236[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Overview  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   The timeout originates from unbounded scans over malformed or random inputs in [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtwo core areas:  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Header detection loops in PDFParser [0m[1;39m([0m[39mparsePDFHeader/parseFDFHeader[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m The brute‚Äêforce trailer rebuild in BruteForceParser.bfSearchForObjects [0m[1;39m([0m[39mand [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mits backward EOF scan[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Both can traverse an entire RandomAccessRead stream for invalid data, leading to[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibFuzzer timeouts.  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Preserve Existing Logic  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We must still attempt header detection and lenient trailer rebuild for real [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPDFs.  [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We cannot disable lenient mode outright nor alter harness or fuzz flags.  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We must cap search ranges without changing file formats or public APIs.  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Steps  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. Limit Header Search in PDFParser  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Introduce a constant:  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       private static final int MAX_[0m[1;33mHEAD[0m[39mER_SEARCH_BYTES = [0m[1;36m4096[0m[39m;  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In [0m[1;35mparsePDFHeader[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ‚Ä¢ Add a byte‚Äêcounter. Before each [0m[1;35msource.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, increment bytesRead.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ‚Ä¢ If bytesRead ‚â• MAX_[0m[1;33mHEAD[0m[39mER_SEARCH_BYTES, rewind to start and return false.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Mirror the same logic in [0m[1;35mparseFDFHeader[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Rationale: invalid inputs will now abort header search after [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m KiB instead of [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mscanning the entire file.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. Cap Brute‚ÄêForce Trailer Rebuild in BruteForceParser  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Introduce a constant:  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       private static final long MAX_BRUTE_FORCE_SEARCH_BYTES = [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m;  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m MiB  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In [0m[1;35mbfSearchForObjects[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ‚Ä¢ Compute endOffset = [0m[1;35mMath.min[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35msource.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, MINIMUM_SEARCH_OFFSET + [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMAX_BRUTE_FORCE_SEARCH_BYTES[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ‚Ä¢ Replace the unbounded do/while loop with a [0m[1;35mwhile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcurrentOffset < endOffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloop.  [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ‚Ä¢ Upon reaching endOffset without fully reconstructing object offsets, break [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mout.  [0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In [0m[1;35mbfSearchForLastEOFMarker[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcalled first[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, also limit the backward scan to [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMAX_BRUTE_FORCE_SEARCH_BYTES.  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If the search completes without locating any trailer markers or object [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstreams, throw an IOException indicating ‚ÄúBrute‚Äêforce search limit reached,‚Äù [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcausing parse failure instead of a prolonged scan.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Rationale: real PDFs will contain trailer markers near file end; malformed [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minputs will fail fast within [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m MiB.  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. System Property Overrides [0m[1;39m([0m[39mOptional but Recommended[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Allow users to tune limits via system properties, e.g.:  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       org.apache.pdfbox.pdfparser.maxHeaderSearchBytes  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       org.apache.pdfbox.pdfparser.maxBruteForceSearchBytes  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Default to the constants above.  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Justification  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Bounded loops prevent pathological scans of gigabyte‚Äêsized or random data, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdirectly addressing the libFuzzer timeout.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Real‚Äêworld PDFs rarely place version info beyond the first few kilobytes or [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtrailer markers past the last megabyte.  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The cap preserves legitimate lenient parsing for large but well‚Äêformed PDFs, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile failing quickly on junk.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Side Effects & Mitigations  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Extremely unusual PDFs with version headers beyond [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m KiB or trailers further [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthan [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m MiB from the startxref may no longer parse in lenient mode.  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Users can raise limits via system properties if needed.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No changes to harness, test code, or external dependencies; all existing [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunctionality and tests remain intact.  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Similar bounding exists in getStartxrefOffset [0m[1;39m([0m[39musing DEFAULT_TRAIL_BYTECOUNT[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mso this approach is consistent with existing design patterns.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJNI global refs: [0m[1;36m26[0m[39m, weak refs: [0m[1;36m0[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===[0m[33mIssue[0m[39m===[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue is a libFuzzer timeout [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m encountered [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhen fuzzing the PDF parser. A proposed patch limits the brute-force object search [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto a configurable byte window [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`MAX_BRUTE_FORCE_SEARCH_BYTES`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, replaces the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moriginal `do‚Ä¶while` loop with a bounded `while` loop, and throws an exception if no[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`endobj` marker is found within the limit.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter applying the patch, the build fails with dozens of Java compilation errors [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`<identifier> expected`, `class, interface, or enum expected`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, indicating that [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe patch introduced malformed Java code‚Äîlikely due to misplaced braces or [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeclarations outside of class/method scope.[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fuzzing harness for PDFBox‚Äôs `BruteForceParser` reports a persistent [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeout when scanning certain inputs.  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No Java compile errors were originally present; the code ran but hung or took [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtoo long under libFuzzer.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A new static constant `MAX_BRUTE_FORCE_SEARCH_BYTES` was added just before [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mbfSearchForObjects[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. It reads a system property [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`org.apache.pdfbox.pdfparser.maxBruteForceSearchBytes`, defaulting to [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m MiB.  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Within `[0m[1;35mbfSearchForObjects[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, the old `do‚Ä¶while` loop [0m[1;39m([0m[39mscanning up to the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlast EOF marker[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m was replaced by a `while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcurrentOffset < endOffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` loop, where [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`endOffset` is computed as `[0m[1;35mmin[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35msource.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, MINIMUM_SEARCH_OFFSET + [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMAX_BRUTE_FORCE_SEARCH_BYTES[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - After the loop, logic was added to:  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ‚Äì Record the last object if its closing marker was found;  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ‚Äì Throw an `IOException` if the limit was reached without finding `endobj`;  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ‚Äì Restore the original stream position at the end of the method.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Duplicate calls to `[0m[1;35msource.seek[0m[1;39m([0m[39moriginOffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and an extra closing brace were[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39madded.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Result  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The Maven build reports over [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m errors, including:  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ‚Ä¢ `<identifier> expected` at lines where the new constant and variable [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeclarations appear.  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ‚Ä¢ `class, interface, or enum expected` at many subsequent lines, implying that[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode intended to be inside a method or class body now resides outside of it.  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This indicates unbalanced or misplaced braces, or that declarations were [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minserted in an illegal context.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Areas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Verify the placement of the `MAX_BRUTE_FORCE_SEARCH_BYTES` declaration‚Äîit [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mshould be at class scope, not inside another method or after the class‚Äôs closing [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbrace.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Check the brace balance in and around `[0m[1;35mbfSearchForObjects[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: ensure that the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmethod opens and closes exactly once and that no extra `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` was introduced.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Confirm that the final `[0m[1;35msource.seek[0m[1;39m([0m[39moriginOffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;` appears once at the end of[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe method, and that the method‚Äôs closing brace is correctly positioned.  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Review indentation and diff context to ensure the patch hunk headers [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`@@ [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m-129[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m10[0m[39m +[0m[1;36m129[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m17[0m[39m @@`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m align with the actual file content.  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Examine adjacent methods and class-level boundaries to ensure no unintended [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverlap or nesting occurred.[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNo root causes of the fuzzer timeout or correctness of the search-limiting logic [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mare addressed here‚Äîthis report focuses on the compilation failures introduced by [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe patch.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
