[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Correct placement of the new constant  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove the `MAX_BRUTE_FORCE_SEARCH_BYTES` declaration from inside or around [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe `[0m[1;35mbfSearchForObjects[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Re-insert it at class scope, alongside other static constants [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mimmediately after `MINIMUM_SEARCH_OFFSET`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, ensuring it is enclosed by the class‚Äôs [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mopening `[0m[1;39m{[0m[39m` and the first method, not nested in any method or after the class‚Äôs [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mclosing `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m`.[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Compute a bounded endOffset early in [0m[1;35mbfSearchForObjects[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - At the top of `[0m[1;35mbfSearchForObjects[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, after obtaining `lastEOFMarker` and [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`originOffset`, insert:  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```java[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       long endOffset = [0m[1;35mMath.min[0m[1;39m([0m[39m lastEOFMarker,[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           MINIMUM_SEARCH_OFFSET + MAX_BRUTE_FORCE_SEARCH_BYTES [0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       long currentOffset = MINIMUM_SEARCH_OFFSET;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       boolean endOfObjFound = false;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove any duplicate `currentOffset` initializations from the method [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msignature.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Replace the unbounded do‚Ä¶while loop with a bounded while loop  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Replace:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```java[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       do [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ‚Ä¶original body‚Ä¶[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcurrentOffset < lastEOFMarker && ![0m[1;35mparser.isEOF[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     with:[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```java[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcurrentOffset < endOffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           ‚Ä¶original loop body [0m[1;39m([0m[39mupdating currentOffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m‚Ä¶[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mendOfObjFound[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m once [0m[32m"endobj"[0m[39m is found, exit early[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               break;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Preserve the exact contents of the loop body‚Äîobject detection, offset [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtracking, charset checks‚Äîso as not to alter PDF parsing semantics.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Post-loop logic: record object or signal timeout  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Immediately after the bounded loop:[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```java[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m If an endobj marker was detected, record the last object[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mendOfObjFound && lastObjOffset > [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;35mbfSearchCOSObjectKeyOffsets.put[0m[1;39m([0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               new [0m[1;35mCOSObjectKey[0m[1;39m([0m[39mlastObjectId, lastGenID[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               lastObjOffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m If no endobj marker was found within the limit, abort[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m!endOfObjFound[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               [0m[32m"Brute-force search limit of "[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               + MAX_BRUTE_FORCE_SEARCH_BYTES[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               + [0m[32m" bytes exceeded without finding endobj"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       ```[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This preserves the intent to collect the trailing object when a marker is [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfound, and to raise an exception when the scan window is exhausted.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Restore the stream position exactly once  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove any duplicated `[0m[1;35msource.seek[0m[1;39m([0m[39moriginOffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;` calls introduced by the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatch.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Leave only one `[0m[1;35msource.seek[0m[1;39m([0m[39moriginOffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;` at the very end of [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mbfSearchForObjects[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, just before its closing `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m`.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Verify brace balance  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - After applying the above changes, ensure that:  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ‚Ä¢ Each method has exactly one opening `[0m[1;39m{[0m[39m` and one closing `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m`.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ‚Ä¢ There are no extraneous `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` or missing braces around the modified loop or [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maround the method‚Äôs end.  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ‚Ä¢ The class closing `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` remains singular and correctly positioned after all [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmethods.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Sanity-check the diff context and reapply to the initial codebase  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Confirm the original method signature, import statements, and other [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mclass-level constants remain untouched aside from the above insertions/removals.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Use `git apply` or `patch` against the unmodified source to avoid merging [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39martifacts from the previous patch.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJustification  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Placing `MAX_BRUTE_FORCE_SEARCH_BYTES` at class scope aligns with existing static[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstant declarations and avoids illegal declarations inside methods or outside [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mclasses.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Computing `endOffset` using `lastEOFMarker` maintains the original ceiling [0m[1;39m([0m[39mstop [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mat the PDF‚Äôs end[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, while also enforcing the new byte-limit window.  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Converting the `do‚Ä¶while` into a `while` prevents infinite or excessively long [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mscans under fuzzing, addressing the libFuzzer timeout without changing the loop [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbody‚Äôs logic.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throwing an `IOException` when the window is exceeded cleanly aborts the parser, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mletting higher-level code handle the case.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Restoring the stream position exactly once preserves original behavior and avoids[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mside effects from duplicated seeks.  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Careful brace balancing eliminates the malformed declarations that caused the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJava compile errors.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPotential Side Effects & Mitigation  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The new exception path may bubble up and abort parsing more aggressively; ensure [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcallers of `[0m[1;35mbfSearchForObjects[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` handle `IOException` as before [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe original code[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39malready throws on parse errors[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Using `lastEOFMarker` in the window calculation is consistent with the pre-patch [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbehavior [0m[1;39m([0m[39mstop at EOF[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and does not expand the scan beyond the file length.  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No changes are made to tests, harness code, or external libraries, so existing [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtest suites and fuzzing logic will continue to operate unchanged.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBy preserving core parsing logic and only rearranging the loop structure and [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstant placement, this strategy resolves the compile errors introduced by [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmisplaced braces, and reinstates a correct, bounded scan.  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mReport[0m===                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         # Evaluation Report                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ## Summary                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         The initial issue reported by the fuzzing harness was a libFuzzer timeout when      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         exercising the PDF parsing and text‚Äêextraction code in Apache PDFBox. To address a  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         suspected unbounded brute‚Äêforce search in the PDF parser, a patch was applied to    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         `BruteForceParser.java`. The patch introduced a configurable maximum search byte    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         limit [1m([0m`MAX_BRUTE_FORCE_SEARCH_BYTES`[1m)[0m, shortened the search loop accordingly, and  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         arranged to throw an `IOException` if the last object marker [1m([0m‚Äúendobj‚Äù[1m)[0m was not     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         found within that limit. After applying the patch and rerunning the fuzzer, the     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         same timeout occurred. The provided thread dump shows the main thread still stuck   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         in parsing and text extraction routines, suggesting that the patch did not prevent  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         the long‚Äêrunning behavior observed by libFuzzer.                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ## Description                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m. Initial Issue                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - The fuzzer run halted with the message ‚ÄúERROR: libFuzzer: timeout.‚Äù            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - No exception traceback from PDFBox was printed; instead, the fuzzer reported   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         an overall time exceeded.                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - A full JVM thread dump was captured, indicating that the main thread was       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         active [1m([0mRUNNABLE[1m)[0m deep inside PDFBox parsing and text‚Äêextraction code paths.        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m. Key Observations in the Initial Issue                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - The timeout appears during the call chain triggered by the fuzzer‚Äôs entry      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         point:                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              fuzzer ‚Üí PDFExtractTextFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput ‚Üí PDFTextStripper.getText ‚Üí   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         PDFTextStripper.processPages ‚Üí PDPageTree.iterator ‚Üí PDPageTree.isPageTreeNode ‚Üí    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         COSDictionary.getCOSName                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - The harness code itself is a driver for fuzzing and is not considered the root [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         cause.                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - The lack of a PDFBox exception or StackOverflowError suggests that parsing     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         continues but does not terminate promptly for certain inputs.                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m. Patch Attempt Details                                                            [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++pagesProcessed > MAX_PAGES_TO_PROCESS[0m[1;39m)[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                    [0m[32m"Page processing limit of "[0m[39m + MAX_PAGES_TO_PROCESS + [0m[32m" [0m        [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===[0m[33mIssue[0m[39m===[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe project‚Äôs fuzzing harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlibFuzzer[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m reported a timeout when exercising [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPDFTextStripper. In response, a patch was applied to limit the number of pages [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprocessed in `PDFTextStripper` by introducing a `MAX_PAGES_TO_PROCESS` threshold [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mdefault [0m[1;36m1000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and throwing an `IOException` if exceeded. After rebuilding with [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthis guard in place, the fuzzer run still reported the same timeout error.[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Under libFuzzer, the PDFTextStripper entry point did not complete within the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallotted time, leading to an ‚ÄúERROR: libFuzzer: timeout‚Äù message.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No stack trace was captured, only the timeout indication from the fuzzing [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mharness.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Observations from the Initial Issue  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The timeout implies excessive work or a hang in the PDFTextStripper code path.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The failure is reproducible under the harness but no other failures [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mcrashes/exceptions[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m were logged.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The harness is simply an invocation of PDFTextStripper on arbitrary input; it [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis not modified and not suspected to introduce the hang.[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - File modified: [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/text/PDFTextStripper.java`  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - At the start of the page‚Äêprocessing loop, inserted:[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m protect against excessive or cyclic page trees under fuzzing[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     final int MAX_PAGES_TO_PROCESS = [0m[1;35mInteger.getInteger[0m[1;39m([0m                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     int pagesProcessed = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mPDPage page : pages[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++pagesProcessed > MAX_PAGES_TO_PROCESS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                             [2m                [0m
